d Ligety]]<br>[[Travis Ganong]]<br>[[Lindsey Vonn]]\n| Gold, slalom<br>Gold, giant slalom; Bronze, super combined<br>Silver, downhill<br>Bronze, super G\n|}\n\n===FIS Alpine World Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Athletes\n! Titles\n|-\n| [[1969 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1969]]\n| Marilyn Cochran\n| Giant slalom champion\n|-\n| [[1978 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1978]]\n| Phil Mahre \n| 2nd in overall\n|-\n| [[1979 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1979]]\n| Phil Mahre\n| 3rd in overall\n|-\n| [[1980 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1980]]\n| Phil Mahre\n| 3rd in overall\n|-\n| [[1981 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1981]]\n| Phil Mahre<br>Tamara McKinney\n| Overall champion<br>Giant slalom champion\n|-\n| [[1982 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1982]]\n| Christin Cooper<br>Phil Mahre<br>Steve Mahre\n| 3rd in overall<br>Overall, Slalom, & Giant slalom champion<br>3rd in overall\n|-\n| [[1983 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1983]]\n| Tamara McKinney<br>Phil Mahre\n| Overall & Giant slalom champion<br>Overall & Giant slalom champion\n|-\n| [[1984 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1984]]\n| Tamara McKinney\n| 3rd in overall, slalom champion\n|-\n| [[1995 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1995]]\n| Picabo Street\n| Downhill champion\n|-\n| [[1996 Alpine Skiing World Cup|1996]]\n| Picabo Street\n| Downhill champion\n|-\n| [[2003 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2003]]\n| Bode Miller\n| Combined champion, 2nd in overall\n|-\n| [[2004 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2004]]\n| Bode Miller\n| Giant slalom & Combined champion\n|-\n| [[2005 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2005]]\n| Bode Miller\n| Overall & Super G champion\n|-\n| [[2006 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2006]]\n| Bode Miller\n| 3rd in overall\n|-\n| [[2007 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2007]]\n| Julia Mancuso<br>Bode Miller\n| 3rd in overall<br>Super G champion\n|-\n| [[2008 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2008]]\n| Lindsey Vonn<br>Ted Ligety<br>Bode Miller\n| Overall & Downhill champion<br>Giant slalom champion<br>Overall & Super combined champion\n|-\n| [[2009 Alpine Skiing World Cup|2009]]\n| Lindsey Vonn\n| Ov